<div class="athena_search_empty" style="display: none;">
  <img class="emptyImg" src="../assets/pc/images/search/search-nothing.png" alt="">
  <p class="big-font">Sorry, no products matched the keyword!</p>
  <p class="small-font">·Use more general terms</p>
  <p class="small-font" style="text-indent: -0.2rem;">·Check your spelling</p>
